### Salud del gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Listar calendarios (filtro por organizer)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/calendars?organizer=Escuela%20de%20Ingenieria

### Crear calendario
POST http://localhost:8080/api/calendars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Conferencias 2025",
  "organizer": "Escuela de Ingenieria",
  "organizerEmail": "org@example.com",
  "description": "Agenda academica",
  "startDate": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59.000Z",
  "keywords": ["ingenieria", "conferencias"],
  "notificationChannel": "email"
}

### Listar eventos (filtro por calendar)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events?calendar=64f1a0c2a0b1c2d3e4f56789

