### Listar comentarios (por eventId)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/comments?eventId=64f1a0c2a0b1c2d3e4f56790

### Crear comentario (genera notificacion)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "64f1a0c2a0b1c2d3e4f56790",
