}

### Listar notificaciones no leidas in-app por usuario
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notifications?recipientEmail=org@example.com&channel=in-app&unread=true

### Marcar notificacion leida
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/64f1a0c2a0b1c2d3e4f56791/read

### Eliminar notificacion
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/notifications/64f1a0c2a0b1c2d3e4f56791
